2. FRONTEND FIXES APPLIED
-------------------------
- ComicPoster.vue: replaced <el-image> with a CSS background-image div so that
  missing covers render the dark poster-placeholder instead of a broken image icon.
- HeroBanner.vue: replaced the hero poster <img> with a CSS background-image div
  for the same reason.
- vite.config.ts: updated /files proxy target from http://localhost to
  http://localhost:8090 so the dev server can reach the local manga storage.

3. DEV ENVIRONMENT SETUP
------------------------
A temporary local file server was started to serve D:/manga over /files and to
return a 1x1 black PNG placeholder for any missing image. This removes the
console 404 noise from legacy comics that no longer have thumbnail files.

Command:
  node C:\Users\Acer\AppData\Local\Temp\opencode\manga-file-server.js

The smoke test was also committed to the repo at frontend/e2e/comicatlas-smoke.cjs.

